    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable choice for someone looking for affordable transportation. While the engine and transmission are functional and have been regularly serviced, the car shows clear signs of its age and mileage, including some noticeable scratches and dings on the exterior and visible wear on the interior upholstery. It has been a dependable daily driver, though it lacks the polish of a newer model. All major systems are currently operational, but prospective buyers should expect the typical maintenance needs of a well-used vehicle.",
