    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, dependable condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a consistent maintenance record. The interior is clean with only minimal signs of use. On the exterior, the paint maintains a nice luster, though you will notice some minor surface scratches and a couple of small door dings upon close inspection. It\u2019s a reliable choice for anyone seeking a quality car that is ready for the road.",
