    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for your next big project! This car is looking for a dedicated owner who can give it the TLC it needs to get back on the road. While it's currently in poor condition and will require some significant mechanical and cosmetic work, it's a fantastic opportunity for a mechanic or hobbyist looking for a rewarding restoration project at a great price!",
